190
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:28,750
Hluboce se omlouvám, pokud to vypadalo,

191
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:30,360
že si pohrávám s tvým životem.

192
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,990
Hned to ukončím.

193
00:11:31,990 --> 00:11:34,210
Hado 4: Byakurai.

194
00:11:47,810 --> 00:11:48,910
Ishido!

195
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:52,130
Inoue, vyleč Ishidova zranění.

196
00:11:52,130 --> 00:11:53,180
Ale…

197
00:11:53,690 --> 00:11:56,200
